      p Datica leads the industry in both security and compliance management. Powered by the Datica Cloud Compliance Management System, Datica's managed compliance service includes:
      ul
        li Intrusion detection review and remediation.
        li Vulnerability scanning management, remediation and proaction.
        li Compliance reporting for HITRUST, SOC 2 and GDPR made available to all CCMS users.
      / p The compliance dashboard is home to all of your compliance data and reporting. The dashboard gives compliance admins incredible insight into their organization’s cloud environments.
      / ul
      /   li Run reports for HITRUST, GDPR, GxP and more.
      /   li Manage your compliance tools in one place. We know compliance admins are not developers, that’s why we provide logging and monitoring data in a simple, usable format within the CCMS.

